"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:1.2.1\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">1.2.1</span> 标题：羊圈、羊栏（sheep pen, sheepfold）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：בָּצְרָה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：botsrah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic2:12\">MIC 2:12</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：גְּדֵרָה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：gidroth, gidroth ts’on)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num32:16\">NUM 32:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num32:24\">NUM 32:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num32:36\">NUM 32:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam24:4\">1SA 24:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer49:3\">JER 49:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph2:6\">ZEP 2:6</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：מִכְלָא</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：mikla’, mikl’oth, mikl’oth ts’on)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps50:9\">PSA 50:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:70\">PSA 78:70</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab3:17\">HAB 3:17</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：מִשְׁפְּתַיִם, שְׁפַתַּיִם</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：mishpthayim, shfatayim)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen49:14\">GEN 49:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg5:16\">JDG 5:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps68:14\">PSA 68:14</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：αὐλή</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：aulē)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:1\">JHN 10:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:16\">JHN 10:16</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：μάνδρα</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：mandra)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt2:26\">JDT 2:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt3:3\">JDT 3:3</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述和用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0930_sheepfold.jpg\" alt=\"石栅栏在夜间保护羊群\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">石栅栏在夜间保护羊群 (© Free Bible Images © David Padfield)</figcaption></figure>羊圈是用石头墙或者树枝和荆棘围起来的一个地方，有一个狭窄的开口供绵羊通过，这个开口可以用灌木丛或牧羊人的身体挡住。晚上，牧人将羊赶入圈中，以保护它们不受盗贼或野兽的侵害。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻译</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>“羊圈”经常需要译为：“保护羊群的地方”、“羊待的地方，周围建有围墙”，或“羊的围栏”。与下一个词条（<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">1.2.2 牲畜棚、牲畜围栏 (animal pen, stall)&lt;REALIA:1.2.2&gt;</a> ）不同，这个围栏建在羊群吃草的区域内，而不是在房屋附近。很多时候，羊圈只是一个临时搭建的构筑物。</p>\n<p>在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer49:3\">JER 49:3</a> 中，希伯来文<em>gderoth</em> 被译为“羊圈”（“sheep-pens”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Jerusalem Bible (1985)\">NJB</abbr> ）或“羊栏”（“sheepfolds”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Jewish Publication Society Version\">NJPSV</abbr> ）。有些译本将这个词译为“墙”（“walls”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New International Version (1984)\">NIV</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New American Standard Bible\">NASB</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Century Version\">NCV</abbr> ），或“树篱”（“hedges”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Living Translation\">NLT</abbr> ）。然而，还有一些译本将希伯来文本做了一个小小的改变，该词的意思因之变为“被划伤遮盖”，表示哀悼。采用这种解法的译本将这节经文第四行的后半部分译为：“哀号，用鞭子抽打自己”（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Revised Standard Version (1989)\">NRSV</abbr> 直译），或“划破你们的身体”（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised English Bible (1989)\">REB</abbr> 直译）。</p>\n<p>希伯来文<em>mishpthayim</em> 和<em>shfatayim</em> 有几种译法。在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen49:14\">GEN 49:14</a> 中，<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> 和<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Jewish Publication Society Version\">NJPSV</abbr> 将其译为“sheepfolds”（“羊圈”），而<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised English Bible (1989)\">REB</abbr> 译作“cattle pens”（“牛栏”）。这些译本认为这些词是指家畜的围栏。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 和<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New International Version (1984)\">NIV</abbr> 将其译为“saddlebags”（“鞍袋、马褡裢”），这是《〈创世记〉手册》（<em>A Handbook on Genesis</em> ）第1090页所推荐的译法。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
